  "texts": [
    "Subsequently, inputs are passed on to a neural network with onedimensional convolutions that pool CNN features using the attention mechanism.",
    "In line with the approach detailed in 13, our training of CAML included early stop when there was no improvement in micro-averaged F1 score for 10 consecutive epochs, with a maximum epochs of 50.",
    "All default hyperparameters were kept, except for max_seq_length which was set to 512.",
    "ClinicalBERT was built upon BioBERT, a domain-specific BERT model pre-trained on PubMed abstracts and full-text articles from PubMed Central 16.",
    "ClinicalBERT performed further pretraining of BioBERT using 2 million clinical notes from MIMIC-III 34."
  ],
